#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Public application form for artists who want to join the Agnosis network. "
"Submits to the admission REST endpoint. Place this on your /join/ page."
msgstr ""
"Öffentliches Bewerbungsformular für Künstler, die dem Agnosis-Netzwerk "
"beitreten möchten. Sendet an den REST-Endpunkt für die Aufnahme. Platziere "
"das auf deiner /join/-Seite."

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "join"
msgstr "beitreten"

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "apply"
msgstr "bewerben"

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "application"
msgstr "Bewerbung"

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "admission"
msgstr "Aufnahme"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Newsletter Popover"
msgstr "Newsletter-Popover"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Icon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter "
"signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer "
"template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled "
"(Settings → Newsletter)."
msgstr ""
"Symbol-Button, der ein Popover über die gesamte Ansicht öffnet, das das "
"Newsletter-Anmeldeformular enthält. Eigenständig — direkt in einen Header- "
"oder Footer-Template-Part einfügen; wird nicht angezeigt, wenn der "
"öffentliche Newsletter deaktiviert ist (Einstellungen → Newsletter)."

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "newsletter"
msgstr "Newsletter"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "subscribe"
msgstr "abonnieren"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "popover"
msgstr "Popover"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "footer"
msgstr "Footer"

#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Newsletter Signup"
msgstr "Newsletter-Anmeldung"

#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Email signup form for the public newsletter (double opt-in). Submits to the "
"newsletter subscribe REST endpoint."
msgstr ""
"E-Mail-Anmeldeformular für den öffentlichen Newsletter (Double-Opt-in). "
"Sendet an den REST-Endpunkt zum Newsletter-Abonnement."

#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "signup"
msgstr "anmelden"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "My Submissions"
msgstr "Meine Einreichungen"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Lists the logged-in artist's pending artwork submissions for review and "
"approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Listet die ausstehenden Kunstwerk-Einreichungen des angemeldeten Künstlers "
"zur Prüfung und Freigabe auf. Platziere das auf deiner /my-"
"submissions/-Seite oder in einem Site-Editor-Template."

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "submissions"
msgstr "Einreichungen"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "review"
msgstr "Prüfung"
